<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Document</title>
  <!-- bootstrap -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../assets/bootstrap-5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <script type="text/javascript" src="../assets/bootstrap-5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
  <!-- font-->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../assets/fontawesome-free-6.1.1-web/css/all.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../assets/fontawesome-free-6.1.1-web/js/all.min.js">
  <!-- css -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../assets/css/common.css">
  <!-- jqury -->
  <script type="text/javascript" src="../assets/js/commonui.js"></script>
  <!-- components -->
  <script src="../assets/js/includeHTML.js"></script>
  <script src="http://code.jquery.com/jquery-latest.js"></script>
</head>
<body>

  <div id="viewWrap">
    <!-- content-wrap S-->
    <div class="content-wrap">
      <!-- header S-->
      <header include-html="/components/header.html"></header>
      <!-- header E-->
      
      <!-- sign-in -->
      <div class="section sign">
        <div class="inner">
          <div class="tit">회원가입</div>
          <div class="form-box">
            <form role="form" class="text-start" action="/sign_up/sign_up2" method="post">
              <div class="login-message">이미 계정이 있으신가요?&nbsp;<a href="/login">로그인</a></div>
              <div class="login-user-wrap">
                <div class="input-box">
                  <label>이메일</label>
                  <input type="email" placeholder="이메일을 입력해 주세요" value="" name="_email" required>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="login-user-wrap">
                <div class="input-box">
                  <label>이메일 확인</label>
                  <input type="email" placeholder="이메일을 다시 한번 입력해 주세요" value="">
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="login-user-wrap">
                <div class="input-box">
                  <label>비밀번호</label>
                  <input type="password" placeholder="비밀번호를 입력해 주세요" name="_pass" id="pass" required>
                </div>
                <p>
                  <span>비밀번호는 영문 대소문자/소문자,숫자,특수문자를 포함하여 8자 ~ 16자 사이로 정해야 합니다.</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="login-user-wrap">
                <div class="input-box">
                  <label>비밀번호 확인</label>
                  <input type="password" placeholder="비밀번호를 다시 한번 입력해 주세요" id="pass2" required>
                </div>
                <p>
                  <span>비밀번호는 영문 대소문자/소문자,숫자,특수문자를 포함하여 8자 ~ 16자 사이로 정해야 합니다.</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="login-user-wrap">
                <div class="input-box">
                  <label>지갑주소</label>
                  <input type="text" placeholder="지갑주소를 입력해 주세요" value="" name="_address" required>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="login-user-wrap">
                <div class="form-check check-box">
                  <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" value="" id="check">
                  <label class="form-check-label" for="check">
                    <a href="#">개인정보취급방치 서비스이용약관</a>에 동의하며, 만 18세 이상 입니다.
                  </label>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="login-user-wrap">
                <button type="submit" class="submit-btn" id="submit" disabled>동의하고 회원가입</button>
              </div>
              
              <script>
                $("#pass2").keyup(function(){
                  var pass = $("#pass").val()
                  var pass2 = $("#pass2").val()
                  if(pass == pass2){
                    $("#submit").attr("disabled", false)
                  }else{
                    $("#submit").attr("disabled", true)
                  }
                })
              </script>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div> 
</body>
<script>
  includeHTML();
  // header
  $(document).on('click', '#header .profile-btn', function(){
    if($('.profile-modal').hasClass('active')){
        $('.profile-modal').removeClass('active').addClass('inactive');
    } else {
        $('.profile-modal').removeClass('inactive').addClass('active');
    }
  })
</script>
</html>